## PROJECT
Hastara is a multi-platform AI palmistry + numerology + astrology app.
Turborepo monorepo: apps/mobile (Expo 51), apps/web (Next.js 15), services/ (Supabase Edge Functions).
Shared logic lives exclusively in packages/ — never duplicate in apps/.

## HARD RULES
- TypeScript strict, no `any`, no `.js` files
- All AI calls server-side only (Edge Functions) — never in client bundle
- pnpm only (not npm, not yarn)
- NativeWind className on mobile — no StyleSheet.create()
- Subscription gating enforced on the server (tRPC middleware), not just client UI
- All AI outputs cached in Redis by reading_id before returning to client
- RLS handles per-user isolation at DB level — always filter by userId in queries too

