## SUBSCRIPTION TIERS
free → standard+love readings (3/mo), oracle, basic numerology
mystic → +career/health, unlimited, birth chart, Chaldean
oracle → +spiritual, rare markings, voice, infographic, triple convergence
sage → +crystal ball, future-self, past-life, mandala, mantra/mudra

Gate UI: `useSubscriptionStore(s => s.canAccessFeature('feature_name'))`
Gate API: `.use(requireTier('oracle'))` on tRPC procedure

